interesting points: The objects disappeared from view after 15 seconds,The sighting was visual with no physical evidence,The objects were observed at a location with recorded coordinates,Details mention multiple observation reports from the Project Blue Book archives,Reported sightings included descriptions of unusual flight characteristics.
sighted object: three round white luminous objects in the sky
witness description: Civilians working in the Aero Maintenance Section at Nellis AF Base
